	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>Re: NESICIDE</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I forgot I also:<br /><br />ChangeLog:<br />1. Added support for soft versus hard emulator resets.  Emulator now passes mapper 28 automated tests entirely.<br />2. Updated Code Editor to QScintilla 2.6.3 snapshot.<br /><br />Problems:<br />There is an issue with the Scintilla editor regarding annotations and the vertical scrollbar.  Mixed-mode C source files do not display proper scrollbar.  If you're working on a C project it's recommended [for now] to turn off mixed-mode annotations.  I upgraded to the latest QScintilla but this problem is still present.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


